SPOT is a customizable graphic illuminated panel to distinguish your own center, backlit with color cycles synchronized with other Iso Benessere equipment.‎

TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS﻿
Supply voltage: 230V±10%, 50/60Hz N∼ | Power Absorption max.‎ 30W.‎

FEATURES INCLUDED:

High power LED customizable color cycles;
RGB synchronization via cable with other Iso Benessere equipment.‎

OPTIONALS AVAILABLE:

Customizable graphics on indication provided at the time of purchase;
Receiver board for wireless color cycle synchronization;
Remote control for RGB color management (available if SPOT is not combined with another Iso Benessere equipment).‎

