FLEXY1 is a professional beauty, massage, and relaxation bed with an elegant design, equipped with manual movement adjustment, removable armrests and headrests, a comfortable mattress, and high-capacity shelves for storing equipment, towels, and everything necessary to keep the cabin efficient and organized.‎

TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS
Maximum load: 200kg.‎

FEATURES INCLUDED:

Structure in precious Natural Teak wood;
Skai mattress in cream color with face hole;
Manual adjustment of the backrest;
Manual adjustment of the legs;
Removable armrests and headrest.‎

